**How to apply css into react app:-
**Ways:-
1.External Css-index.css.

2.sass/scss:- 
 --Writing css with superpowers.
 --Writing Advance css.


3.Styled-Components:-
 --To write css to our components.

** material UI--React library  --prebuild css
**Bootstrap -- React library --prebuild css
**Chakra UI:-
**Ant Design:- 2nd most popular library.

**Tailwind CSS:-
 --Building modern css without leave your html.
 --It works with all frameworks.

 **Installation:-
  -- npm install -D tailwindcss postcss 
  --postcss means transform your css with javascript.

  --npx tailwindcss init -- created tailwind.config.js file
   --postcssrc -- created configuration file for postcssrc.

   **Tailwind Css:- Provide classname to apply css.